Package org.flag4j.arrays.backend

Interface CooMatrixMixin<T extends CooMatrixMixin<T,U,V,W,X,Y>,U extends DenseMatrixMixinOld<U,T,W,X,Y>,V extends SparseVectorMixin<V,W,T,U,X,Y>,W extends DenseVectorMixin<W,V,U,X,Y>,X,Y>

Type Parameters:
T - Type of this sparse matrix.
U - Type of dense matrix which is equivalent to T.
V - Type of vector similar to T.
W - Type of dense vector equivalent to V.
X - Storage for entries of this tensor.
Y - Type (or wrapper of) an individual element in the matrix.
All Superinterfaces:
MatrixMixinOld<T,U,V,W,X,Y>, MatrixVectorOpsMixin<T,V,W>, SparseTensorMixin<U,T>, TensorBinaryOpsMixin<T,T>, TensorMixin<T,X,Y>
All Known Implementing Classes:
CooCMatrix, CooFieldMatrix, CooFieldMatrixBase, CooMatrix
